{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act12mini_level_act12mini_st01","storyGroup":"act12mini","storySort":1,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"荒舍","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act12mini_st01","storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act12mini/level_act12mini_st01","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"next":1,"characters":["年老的村民","玛恩纳","托兰","切斯柏","热情的村民","贵族的私兵","国民院代表","赏金猎人","染病的流民","大骑士长"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"dialog","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"在过去的某个时刻，骑士击碎浪潮的故事尚未被写成小说，穿过林海的风中还能听见炮火轰鸣，弓弦振响。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"那时人们笃信自己困于黑暗，以生死之重掷向大地，以淋漓鲜血作为生存的代价和谏言。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"而如今，深秋的日色在原野上缓慢地舒展，农人的铁锤叮叮敲打，赶在下一场风雨之前将房檐修葺。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"山脚的墓园中，人们只是挥动铁器，一铲一铲翻开泥土，伴随着啜泣声，将枯萎的作物埋进地里。","id":13},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":19},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":20,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"11月27日 3:20 P.M.","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"卡西米尔南部乡野","id":24},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......所以，先生，您现在也是一个人在四处游荡了？","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"没有侍从，没有追随者，甚至也没有剑与甲胄......但似乎也没有人与您为敌。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"我还记得，当年许多人说，您是在和这个国家排得上名号的家族作对，总会惹上大麻烦的。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"character","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#11$1","fadetime":"1","id":35},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"这么说的那些人，不也接受了可能给他们带来麻烦的救济物资吗？","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......我已经离开了权势者如今勾心斗角的场地，不再值得他们分神顾忌。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"是啊，是啊......您应该不觉得意外。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"就像当年我逃来这片异国的土地，以为那位君王的法术会永远在我背后穷追不舍......","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......但是现在，您看，我这手无寸铁的教书匠，在一间连风雨都抵御不了的小屋里，已经风平浪静地生活了二十余年啦。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"你自称来自莱塔尼亚......巫王高塔早已倒塌，你为什么还留在这里？","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"我躲藏太久啦，如今已经没有非得回到什么地方生活的心气。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"消息流传到这样偏远的地方花了不少时间，而我发现自己已经习惯了在田野间劳作、只计算自己温饱的日子。","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"而且为了伪装，我早已将角斩断，习惯像库兰塔一样生活。就算莱塔尼亚还有我的故人幸存，他们又该怎么认我？","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"但你始终以莱塔尼亚人自居。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"哎，先生，我只是个忘不掉前半辈子的可怜人。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"热忱者已经早早死去，我这样躲躲藏藏活到最后的，也无所谓自己是什么面目了。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"您是来故地重游的吗？我拿不出什么东西，但您如果愿意接受一杯热茶的招待，我荣幸之至。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"不必了。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"好，好......先生，我只是一直记得您的恩情。这些年了。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"其他人以卡西米尔的地区方言互相呼唤的时候，您看出了我的窘迫。但您没有揭穿我自称的身份，默许我继续站在流民的队伍里。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......看来您不记得了。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"您对我说的事情都没有印象，刚刚被认出来的时候却也不觉得惊讶......那您应该像这样救过许多人吧。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......都过去太久了。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#4$1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"你在帮人写告示？","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"您说刚才那张？是啊，安全告示。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"有骑士昨天来过我们村子，说是最近有强盗一类的人流窜到这一带来了，连茨沃涅克城内都出现了袭击案。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"但明眼人都知道，只是有强盗的话，我们这样远离移动城市航道的村庄就算真的遭受洗劫，也不会有人在意。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"因此，征战骑士如此郑重的提醒，总让我觉得惴惴不安哪。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"先生，即使现在没有人向您寻仇，您也还是带上一把武器更合适。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......这是征战骑士告诉你们的？","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"原来您还没有听说？","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"说来确实奇怪。这几年来，我竟然真的见到征战骑士在关心平民百姓的死活。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"像是前两年村子里搬来的几户人家，就是骑士从天灾底下抢救出来的、隔壁集镇的幸存者......","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#9$1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......我不是奇怪这些事。这是他该做的。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_31_g4_mini12_village.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":103},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你可把我们吓坏了，切斯柏。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"要不是你及时把头盔摘下来，说不好就有村民吓得对你拉弓了。","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#10$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"万一不小心伤到了您这位尊贵的征战骑士......嗯，虽说挂在我身上的罪名已经不少了，但悬赏令估计还能再加急一些。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"“村民”？哈哈......","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"幸好你们还记得我这张脸。","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......呃，至少大多数人还记得？","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"活着的人里，你的老熟人不多啦，新来的倒是不少。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"犯不着为我们这些人愁眉苦脸的。有何贵干？都巡逻到荒地上的小村庄了，总不能是因为最近可忙的事情不多吧？","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"毕竟，我听说这一带现在不太安宁，征战骑士在协助维护城外的秩序......","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"——我们几个弟兄还在您手下接受调查。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......所以我才找来这里，托兰。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"既然过来的赏金猎人是你在牵头，那话就好说多了。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"你知道的，我得先按照纪律办事。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"难得你这次说的不是“只按照纪律办事”。那我们单独聊聊？","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"上次碰面时“小矿工”就想跟你叙叙旧，可惜当时我们忙着撤退，你忙着按纪律回队报告......他前两年就病死啦。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":138},{"type":"character","id":139},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_bg_bg_indoor_u.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"从这里望下去......正好能看见河谷对面的工业园区。你们的据点可真是选了个好位置。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#4$1","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"喔，看起来是家大企业。怎么了？","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那里原本是帕伦尼斯科家族的庄园。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......怀旧了？","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"多少有点。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......说回正题吧。我不知道猎人们对我有多大的敌意，但我不希望你在他们面前为难。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"这你倒是可以放心，就算这里有许多人不是咱们的老朋友......他们也不至于自不量力到试图谋杀一位全副武装的骑士团长。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#5$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"不，不是担心埋伏......呃，我以为我还没有告诉过你晋升的事？","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"别这么惊讶嘛。虽说征战骑士内部的事情相对算是机密，但你都当上团长好几年了，猎人们总该有点情报。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#4$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"比如说什么“能刺碎星光的黑枪”啦，“向天灾冲锋的骑士”啦。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"行了行了，你说的这些“情报”我实在担当不起，而且追击自己叛变的同僚，也不是什么光彩的事情。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"你明知道我这点武艺不算什么，真正值得一提的功绩更是寥寥。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#4$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我倒是知道你一定会这么说。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"唉，你啊......","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"所以，最近的袭击事件，你是真的听到了什么风声，还是上面要你们配合做做样子？","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"为城里的事情调动城外的征战骑士，这可不多见。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......二者皆有吧。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"托兰，我向你保证，猎人们会安然无恙地被释放。把他们抓起来的是巡逻的征战骑士，你我之间原本是不该有这种误会的。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"当然啦，你可不会冤枉清白无辜的人。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"虽然我们不能说自己行为端正，但最近的袭击事件倒确实和我们没什么关系。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......但我必须请你再等一等，等到这段时间的调查结束，我才能放走他们。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我相信你说的“这段时间”不会太长。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......这种事情，你写封信给我就够了。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"专程来找我，是想说什么？","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......你的猎人，那个独眼的札拉克，跟我解释过你们来这里的原因了。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"嗯哼，我觉得他应该没敢跟您说假话。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"他说你们收到了一些村民的求助信。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"虽说民间组织的名号只是收集情报用的一个幌子，但对于开得起好价格的求助人，咱们偶尔也乐意帮帮忙。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"这可是大实话，我们确实是来帮忙的。只不过用的手段呢，可能不那么高尚。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......我明白你要做的是件好事，所以我才愧疚。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"听着，托兰......我希望你们至少能暂缓行动，不要被牵涉进此次调查。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"这次承接茨沃涅克城区改造建设的几家企业，尽量都别接近。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......听起来是大事件啊。有人要借你们的手铲除异己了？","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哈，多谢劝告。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"既然你都说到这个份上了，那我答应。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哎，不介意我先去跟兄弟们说一声吧？不然这会儿他们该动手把某些可怜的家伙绑架回来了。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":218},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......好啦，再说说你腰间挂着的那柄佩剑吧？","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"鉴于咱们那位骑士老爷这么多年都没换过武器，我应该不会认错。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你见到玛恩纳了？","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":228},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"character","id":230},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":231},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":232},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":234,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......您没有听说这一带最近的乱象也很正常，先生。您取道荒野走过来，还没有靠近过茨沃涅克吧。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"如果路上也没有偶遇信使、买一两份报纸的话，就更无从得知近期的新闻了......","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":240},{"type":"character","id":241},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","fadetime":"1","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"——索默老师，您在这儿呢。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"告示已经贴出去啦。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"喔，是小艾瓦，辛苦你了。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"不辛苦不辛苦，难得能给老师帮上忙！","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"——就是，我想顺带问一下，跟您聊天的这位老爷是......？","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"嗯......是位了不起的骑士。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"喔！欢迎欢迎。我呀，看您站在这里有一会儿了，是来看地的吗？","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"听说最近有不少骑士老爷想在城外买块地休假用，都快成为新的潮流了。","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"我们这儿没遇到过天灾，附近的村子里也都没有感染者，可干净了。","id":260,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"或者您是代表企业来的？我今天早晨还在报纸上见到盖尔工业的招聘启事，说是为了茨沃涅克的新城区建设，要招不少人。","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"只要是他们觉得能干活儿的人，就算是感染者也可以获得机会，去城市里生活。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"唔......盖尔工业有赞助骑士团吗？","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......咳，小艾瓦啊。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"我刚想起这里有封信要交给村长。能请你再帮我个忙吗？","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_004#1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"嗯？好啊，没问题。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的村民","text":"现在就去？好呀。","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_004.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":277},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":278},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"哈哈，真不好意思......只是他们最近对城里来的人都特别感兴趣，就顾不上讲礼貌了。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"您是从北边那条路过来的，应该看到河谷那边崭新的工厂了。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"比较接近城市航道的沥泉村和垒石村，听说最近也把地卖出去了。这些消息都是之前来收税金的人告诉大家的。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"所以现在许多人梦想着村庄被企业看中，土地被收购，然后自己就能拿到进入城市生活的本金。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......荒唐。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"是啊，荒唐的期盼。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"我已经足够老迈，不需要生活有所期盼。可是像他们那样的孩子，有个白日梦也比什么都没有要好。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......先生，我原本是因言获罪，才仓皇出逃。曾经在莱塔尼亚，我也是高塔贵族宴席上高谈阔论的学究。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"但如今我已白发苍苍，头脑中的想法只囿于眼前的温饱，因为这就足够消耗掉我全部的精力。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"他们的处境与我无异。一个虚无的梦想就能撑满他们抬头向上张望时全部的视野。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......我无意指责。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"即使真有人可以承担指责，那也不在此处。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"故地重游，我怕您失望。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......我只是来找人才路过这里。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"你见过两位金色的征战骑士吗？","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"金色？这几年附近出现过的征战骑士，大都是银甲银枪，至于其中有没有例外......抱歉，我记不太清了。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"不必回想了......见过他们的人不会忘记。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"可您就这么漫无目的地找吗？要是有什么线索，我可以帮您想些办法，或者为您指个路。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#10$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"这些年有工程车队来过吗？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"嗯？......没有。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"那就不用指路了。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......我记得。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_4064_mlynar_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":325},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_31_g4_mini12_village.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":326},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":327},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_217","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族的私兵","text":"我们记住你了，临光家的小子......你今天让老爷出的丑，我们会百倍地从你同情的那些贱骨头身上讨回来！","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_217.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":334},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_bg_bg_23_G05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":335},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":336},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":337},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_222","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"国民院代表","text":"为了平息舆论，我们完全可以通过这项立法。但你应该知道，司法的触角远未伸到偏远的荒野上。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_npc_222.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"国民院代表","text":"只要没有你，这些人的声音根本到不了大骑士领。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_npc_222.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":344},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_bg_bg_forest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":345},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008#1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"够了，停下来吧，这支队伍已经走得够远了。","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008#1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"就算我们可以跟着你一直打下去，卡西米尔也永远不会有你期望的，能让我们跟你这样的贵族老爷平起平坐的地方。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":355},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_bg_bg_barracks.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":356},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"染病的流民","text":"救、救命......！骑士老爷，我见过的骑士老爷，求求你们......来救救我......","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_avg_npc_626_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"染病的流民","text":"我不能死在帐篷里！我的孩子明天早上就要回来了......我不能......","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_avg_npc_626_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":366},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_bg_bg_kxstreet.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":367},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_210_1#1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大骑士长","text":"抱歉，玛恩纳。我无法回答你。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_avg_npc_210_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":373},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":374},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":375},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":376},{"type":"background","id":377},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":379},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_trainwhistle","volume":"1","id":380},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":381},{"type":"text","text":"尖锐的鸣笛声传来，谈话的二人各自后退了一步。","id":382},{"type":"character","id":383},{"type":"dialog","id":384},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_31_mini12_i3.png","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","x":"-80","y":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"0.9","yScaleFrom":"0.9","xScaleTo":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.85","xFrom":"-80","xTo":"0","duration":"20","block":"false","id":386},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"5","block":"false","id":387},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":388},{"type":"text","text":"商业联合会的大型运载车驶过，货箱上庞大的白色标识喷漆逼视着站在路边的行人。","id":389},{"type":"text","text":"车轮碾过坑坑洼洼的土路，扬起一路烟尘，引擎的轰鸣被风吹向深秋的原野。","id":390},{"type":"text","text":"无剑的骑士沉默着。","id":391},{"type":"text","text":"他与钢铁的巨物对视许久，直到自己被抛下。","id":392},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"4","id":393},{"type":"dialog","id":394},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":395},{"type":"character","id":396},{"type":"text","text":"然后他转过身，沿着既定的道路缓步向前走去。","id":397},{"type":"text","text":"在深深浅浅的车辙旁边，骑士的步伐未曾留下任何痕迹。","id":398},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":400},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":401},{"type":"image","id":402},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005#1","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"先生......？","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......唉。","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......那位卡西米尔的骑士......为什么看起来如此失望？","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"为什么他放下了剑......为什么又还愿意向前走呢？","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年老的村民","text":"......二十多年了，或许我也该答应小艾瓦，陪她出去看看。","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":411},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"character","id":413},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_31_g4_mini12_village.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":414},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":415},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":417},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......就在那边的工厂附近，我们碰巧遇到。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#4$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那可真是......值得怀旧。","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"他怎么在这种地方？","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"大概是迷路了吧？毕竟上一次来也是那么多年前了。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#3$1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哈，这话你当着他的面说试试？","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那还是饶了我吧。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我还以为他会往乌萨斯走呢，毕竟他是为了寻亲才离开大骑士领的。","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"但我记得当年我们就猜测过，他的兄长在家书里描述的北风和雪原，也许只是编造出来的景色，对吧？","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那两位令人尊敬的骑士实际去了哪里，本来也只有监正会的高层才清楚。","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"看来，你在征战骑士的队伍里这些年，也没再听到过任何风声？","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"很遗憾。","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"放不下这件事的也不止他一个人......","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我隐约记得，前两天夜里还梦见过我们聚在一起，讨论那两位失踪的临光。","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......那就当他只是出来度个假吧。","id":444,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"这么多年了一点消息都没有，玛恩纳他又不傻。","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"对了，你跟他说了最近这一带治安不太好的事情吗？说不定他顺手就帮你解决了呢。","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"是，我确实期望他能出手相助，所以才帮他把武器带给骑士团的工匠调整一下。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"喔， 你这样讲究武器的人，确实该看不下去了。","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"就算他的工作不用剑，临光家在大骑士领总该有几个熟识的工匠，能顺手帮他保养一下武器吧？","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"有倒是有。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"比如说，咱们去掺和与乌萨斯的冲突的那段时间，我不是被玛恩纳指挥着联络过一些骑士团？","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"其中那几位后来管我的猎人们叫“萨卡兹骑士团”的，都是临光家的老熟人啦。","id":459,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"跟过西里尔，跟过斯尼茨，也见过他玛恩纳穿行战火之中，意气风发的样子。","id":461,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"还有一个工匠呢，是他自己的小侄女，年轻得都搞不懂他在做什么，还差点把自己也搅进骑士竞技那摊浑水。","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你猜以玛恩纳的脾气，他会不会去请这些人帮忙？","id":465,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"哈哈。","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我倒是觉得，他本来是可以去请的。","id":469,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......你觉得他还用得着自己的剑吗？","id":471,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"他还愿意“帮忙解决麻烦事”吗？并非出于旧情，只是作为骑士而伸出援手。","id":473,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......怎么突然这样问？","id":475,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......因为我这里有些私人恩怨。","id":477,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"有十年时间里，我将前一任骑士团长视作恩师，他不过问出身，也不在乎我得罪过哪些贵族。我因此对他十分敬重。","id":479,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"直到我接过他的位置，也接过了整个骑士团的文书记录。","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那时我才清楚看见，在我所恪守的骑士训令背后，竟然也写满中饱私囊的权钱交易。","id":483,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我并不是在指控整个卡西米尔的征战骑士......只是我自己的处境，已经与高洁的骑士光辉相去甚远。","id":485,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你真要跟一个赏金猎人说这些？","id":487,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","id":488},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"总得有个老朋友听我说吧。","id":489,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":490},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"你知道，我只想踏踏实实地按规矩行事。","id":491,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"骑士的准则也许在你看来有迂腐之处，但至少它不吃人。","id":492,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......它至少不会容许瑟莉娜枉死。","id":494,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......她不在了？什么时候......？","id":496,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"好几年了。","id":498,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"抱歉，我只是很难跟人提起这件事。","id":500,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......不过，玛恩纳是知道的。当年瑟莉娜被带去大骑士领的时候，我给他写过求助信。","id":502,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"既然是去大骑士领......那可是大麻烦啊。","id":504,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":505},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"所以他无法为瑟莉娜做什么，我也能够理解。我知道害死瑟莉娜的不是他，我也......绝不会迁怒于他。","id":506,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#13$1","id":507},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"只是那时我的去信没有回音，所以今天见面时，我难免旧事重提。","id":508,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":509},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......","id":510,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"如果信件不巧被淹没在那时给西里尔吊唁的去信中，那么是我不够走运。","id":512,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"但他承认收到了我的信，也看过了......如今却选择对过去的一切闭口不谈，也不愿认同我的仇怨。","id":514,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"他是什么时候——连是非黑白都不敢面对了？","id":516,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":517},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"喔......","id":518,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":519},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那么，我先问个小问题。","id":520,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","id":521},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"既然你没打算找赏金猎人们帮忙，却把他算在你为私人恩怨做的计划之中......","id":522,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":523},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"他是你想拉拢的人呢......还是你要报复的人？","id":524,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_625_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#12$1","id":525},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......","id":526,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"请不要误会我。","id":528,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_627_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":529},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":530},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":531},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":532},{"type":"character","id":533},{"type":"image","id":534}],"characters":["年老的村民","玛恩纳","托兰","切斯柏","热情的村民","贵族的私兵","国民院代表","赏金猎人","染病的流民","大骑士长"]}